title: FF RJ - Take Time Out
description:
Summary:

Jess is a college level girl's basketball coach. She doesn't want to acknowledge that she could be gay. Her fear is, if it's found out that she's gay, she won't be able to recruit new basketball players for her team. 

Enter Robin, she's a professor of Economics at the same college with an interest in Jess. Can Jess let go of her fear and have a relationship with Robin?
